    "How comfortable do you think someone outside your religion would be if they saw you: Tell someone you'll pray for him or her" AS how_comfortable_do_you_think_someone_outside_your_religion_would_be_if_they_saw_you_tell_someone_you_ll_pray_for_him_or_her,
    "How comfortable do you think someone outside your religion would be if they saw you: Ask or offer to pray with someone" AS how_comfortable_do_you_think_someone_outside_your_religion_would_be_if_they_saw_you_ask_or_offer_to_pray_with_someone,
    "How comfortable do you think someone outside your religion would be if they saw you: Bring up your religion, unprompted, in conversation" AS how_comfortable_do_you_think_someone_outside_your_religion_would_be_if_they_saw_you_bring_up_your_religion_unprompted_in_conversation,
