    "How comfortable do you think someone outside your religion would be if they saw you: Decline some kind of food or beverage for religious reasons (kosher, halal, fasting rules, etc)" AS how_comfortable_do_you_think_someone_outside_your_religion_would_be_if_they_saw_you_decline_some_kind_of_food_or_beverage_for_religious_reasons_kosher_halal_fasting_rules_etc,
    "How comfortable do you think someone outside your religion would be if they saw you: Wear religious clothing/jewelry (hijab, kippah, wig, kara, turban, cross, etc)" AS how_comfortable_do_you_think_someone_outside_your_religion_would_be_if_they_saw_you_wear_religious_clothing_jewelry_hijab_kippah_wig_kara_turban_cross_etc,
